### Restaurant OS Backend - Phase 4 File Upload Testing
### Note: REST Client doesn't support file uploads well
### Use Postman, Insomnia, or cURL for actual testing

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
@menuItemId = YOUR_MENU_ITEM_ID
@tenantId = YOUR_TENANT_ID

### ============================================
### FILE UPLOAD ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### 1. Upload Menu Item Image (Owner/Manager)
### Use Postman or cURL for this
POST {{baseUrl}}/storage/menu-items/{{menuItemId}}/image
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

# In Postman:
# - Select "Body" tab
# - Choose "form-data"
# - Add key "file" with type "File"
# - Select your image file

### cURL Example:
# curl -X POST \
#   http://localhost:3000/api/storage/menu-items/uuid-here/image \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer your-token" \
#   -F "file=@/path/to/image.jpg"

### ============================================

### 2. Upload Tenant Logo (Owner/Manager)
POST {{baseUrl}}/storage/tenants/{{tenantId}}/logo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

# In Postman:
# - Select "Body" tab
# - Choose "form-data"
# - Add key "file" with type "File"
# - Select your logo file

### cURL Example:
# curl -X POST \
#   http://localhost:3000/api/storage/tenants/uuid-here/logo \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer your-token" \
#   -F "file=@/path/to/logo.png"

### ============================================

### 3. Delete Menu Item Image (Owner/Manager)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/storage/menu-items/{{menuItemId}}/image
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================

### 4. Delete Tenant Logo (Owner/Manager)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/storage/tenants/{{tenantId}}/logo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================

### 5. Access Uploaded File (No Auth Required)
GET http://localhost:3000/uploads/menu-items/menu-item-1234567890-abc123.jpg

### ============================================

### 6. Get Menu Item with Image URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu-items/{{menuItemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Response will include:
# {
#   "id": "uuid",
#   "name": "Pizza",
#   "image": "/uploads/menu-items/menu-item-123-abc.jpg",
#   ...
# }

### ============================================

### 7. Get Tenant with Logo URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Response will include:
# {
#   "id": "uuid",
#   "name": "Restaurant Name",
#   "logo": "/uploads/tenants/tenant-logo-456-def.png",
#   ...
# }

### ============================================
### ERROR SCENARIOS
### ============================================

### 8. Try to upload without file (400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/storage/menu-items/{{menuItemId}}/image
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

### 9. Try to upload as Waiter (403 Forbidden)
# Use waiter token
POST {{baseUrl}}/storage/menu-items/{{menuItemId}}/image
Authorization: Bearer WAITER_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

### 10. Try to upload for non-existent menu item (404 Not Found)
POST {{baseUrl}}/storage/menu-items/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/image
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

### ============================================
### TESTING WITH CURL
### ============================================

### Upload Menu Item Image
# curl -X POST \
#   http://localhost:3000/api/storage/menu-items/YOUR_MENU_ITEM_ID/image \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" \
#   -F "file=@./test-image.jpg"

### Upload Tenant Logo
# curl -X POST \
#   http://localhost:3000/api/storage/tenants/YOUR_TENANT_ID/logo \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" \
#   -F "file=@./test-logo.png"

### Delete Menu Item Image
# curl -X DELETE \
#   http://localhost:3000/api/storage/menu-items/YOUR_MENU_ITEM_ID/image \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN"

### Delete Tenant Logo
# curl -X DELETE \
#   http://localhost:3000/api/storage/tenants/YOUR_TENANT_ID/logo \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN"

### Download Uploaded File
# curl -O http://localhost:3000/uploads/menu-items/menu-item-123-abc.jpg

### ============================================
### TESTING FILE VALIDATION
### ============================================

### Test with file > 5MB (should fail)
# curl -X POST \
#   http://localhost:3000/api/storage/menu-items/YOUR_MENU_ITEM_ID/image \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" \
#   -F "file=@./large-file.jpg"
# Expected: 400 Bad Request - "File size exceeds 5MB limit"

### Test with invalid file type (should fail)
# curl -X POST \
#   http://localhost:3000/api/storage/menu-items/YOUR_MENU_ITEM_ID/image \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" \
#   -F "file=@./document.pdf"
# Expected: 400 Bad Request - "Invalid file type..."

### Test with valid image types (should succeed)
# JPEG: curl -X POST ... -F "file=@./image.jpg"
# PNG:  curl -X POST ... -F "file=@./image.png"
# WebP: curl -X POST ... -F "file=@./image.webp"
